        > Exists as a hybrid entity which draws from high technology
	corporations and compartmented, government, intelligence and military
operations, but which in effect functions as an independent, separate entity
        > Apparently, is controlled by no single branch of conventional
	government, military Service or agency  
        > In general, access to this project is by project-controlled
